{"tid":322223,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"昆頓塔倫天奴以60 年代殺人組織曼森家族拍電影","createTime":"2017-07-14T15:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T11:33:11.000Z","uid":14730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd2ac626f054f6999117d30726677120026f0b6","tid":322223,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/235907_f78aeb1cfd6e05b033613b307678bdb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F235907_f78aeb1cfd6e05b033613b307678bdb2.png&h=8a4d306a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講了又講，話想拍《標殺令》第三集的鬼才導演昆頓塔倫天奴（Quentin Tarantino），又傳出新消息，表示將改編 60 年代末凶殘殺人組織「曼森家族」（Manson Family）虐殺導演波蘭斯基（Roman Polanski）懷孕的妻子兼著名演員 Sharon Tate 一案。消息更指塔倫天奴已經寫好劇本，並打算邀請畢彼特（Brad Pritt）、珍妮花羅倫絲（Jennifer Lawrence）、瑪歌羅比（Margot Robbie）等參演，非常大陣仗。其實「曼森家族」的駭人事蹟早已成為流行次文化的靈感多年，歌影視作品樣樣齊，到底，「曼森家族」有幾邪惡？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「曼森家族」實際上不是一家人，而是以 Charles Manson 為首的殺人組織，成員多為仰慕他的年輕中產女性，當時 Manson 與大概 30 位主要成員群居於一個廢棄農場。年少時已犯案累累的他，其實極度迷戀披頭四，渴望發展音樂事業，阻佢者死，於是後來他派遣追隨者先後殺害 9 個「阻礙」其音樂生涯的人。Sharon Tate 一案正是因為他派人殺一位音樂監製，殊不知該監製早已搬離大宅，轉手給波蘭斯基一家，釀成 Sharon Tate 及其 4 位友人慘死。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ur7vI1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ur7vI1&d=5Cz7%2FRjhriApYT0U1Dyvv6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9d6abc03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ur7vI1</a>"},{"pid":"b941258ee65b51587f08b1b043de493d9108f79f","tid":322223,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:03:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://edvcars.pixnet.net/blog/post/43362908-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%8B%82%E9%AD%94-%3C06%3E-charles-manson-and-manson-fami\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedvcars.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F43362908-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258B%2582%25E9%25AD%2594-%253C06%253E-charles-manson-and-manson-fami&d=5Cz7%2FRjhriApYT0U1Dyvv6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3da3cd27\" target=\"_blank\">http://edvcars.pixnet.net/blog/post/43362908-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%8B%82%E9%AD%94-%3C06%3E-charles-manson-and-manson-fami</a>"},{"pid":"5b2c6b7d82f3714af26437125110e0d2aff93d36","tid":322223,"uid":16344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"佢D戲必睇"}]}